* Iron saw Cheetor suddenly get in the way between Iris and Prowl, thinking 
of how he'd be a dead bot.*

" Cheetor!" she called to him, getting to her feet a little slowly and 
unsteadily.* " Get out of there! You'll be killed!"

* She began to move towards them, hoping that Prowl would just step over him 
or knock him aside, not wantiong to have to pick the kid out of his teeth.*

" You can't stop him! Just get out of the way!"

* Iris looked at Cheetor in surprise, suddenly reaching out to him and try 
to shove him aside.*

" Don't be stupid, kid!"
